<div class="title">I Thought I Was Going to Die</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Julie&Exact=1">Julie</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Julie. "I Thought I Was Going to Die: An Experience with AMT (exp22565)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 2, 2004. erowid.org/exp/22565</div>

<br/>



